WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.280
The Federated Research Data Repository, FRDR.

00:00:05.280 --> 00:00:10.560
This is a national platform designed to help Canadian researchers discover, store, and share research data.

00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:13.200
Our key goals are

00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:18.960
Improve data discoverability, working in partnership with services like Lunaris.

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:24.240
Promote open science practices by supporting the reuse of research data

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:29.200
and ensure the long-term preservation of valuable research outputs.

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:35.840
FRDR is open to researchers across Canada and supports a wide range of disciplines and data types.

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:42.000
Whether you're working in engineering, life sciences, social sciences, or the humanities,

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.160
FRDR provides the infrastructure you need for robust data sharing.

